==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Earning
<hw>Earn"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Earnings</plw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <def>That which is earned; wages gained by work or
services; money earned; -- used commonly in the plural.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>As to the common people, their stock is in their persons and in
their <qex>earnings</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Earpick</ent>⟦br⟧
